ur_Fellows" title="Category:MacArthur Fellows">MacArthur Fellows</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:People_associated_with_energy" title="Category:People associated with energy">People associated with energy</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:People_from_Amherst,_Massachusetts" title="Category:People from Amherst, Massachusetts">People from Amherst, Massachusetts</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Renewable_energy_commercialization" title="Category:Renewable energy commercialization">Renewable energy commercialization</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Sustainability_advocates" title="Category:Sustainability advocates">Sustainability advocates</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
